<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/path/to/your/css/style.css"> <!-- Link to your CSS file -->
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="imgs/logo.png" type="image/x-icon">
  
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        p {
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .button {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 50px;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon">✔️</div>
        <h1>Thank You!</h1>
        <p>Your message has been sent successfully. We will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        <p>If you have any further questions, feel free to <a href="/contact">contact us</a> again.</p>
        <div class="button">
            <a href="/">Go to Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
